docs.text: About To put it shortly, SKRA-D was made by a child brought the name Henry. This WHOLE entire website is more involved in the workings of the useless-games project (the 33rd perhaps). This website is dedicated to strange content my local friends share. Reason Simple. Find a docs template or docs website and build docs. I was "inspired" you might say. I was originally chasing after forums instead, but I had wanted it coded from scratch (hard) so it was scrapped. Authority Uh... (c) Antenning Inc. All rights reserved...? Open-source... ...only to my friends. I don't trust anyone else. Oh, and my brother too. They know how to write markdown and they come up with strange stuff (that's what this website is about)
